data.description: Welcome to effortless, upscale living at White Flint Station! This modern 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom condo is a perfect blend of luxury & convenience. With a fresh coat of paint, and new hardwood floors this home is completely MOVE-IN READY!  Both generously sized bedrooms feature large walk-in closets, and one has an ensuite bathroom. The kitchen is well-appointed, with abundant cabinetry, spacious countertops, and quality stainless steel appliances. Enjoy convenient in-unit laundry and a welcoming balcony overlooking the beautifully landscaped courtyard!  This condo community offers a bounty of amenities, including a sparkling pool, fitness center, & resident lounge.  Nestled in a lush, neighborhood-like complex with significantly lower condo fees than other buildings in the area, it's steps away from Pike and Rose's vibrant shopping & dining and minutes away walking distance to North Bethesda Metro station. Your tranquil yet centrally-located urban retreat awaits!
